3 Level 1 and 5 Level 2 statements for each dimension. This helped me
distinguish the statements a bit more. I did some digging online to see how
other companies define similar values to make it feel more specific to Big
Spaceship, as well.

I was also thinking that fewer statements at first would be better, and we
can increase the number of statements as we see how people respond and get
acclimated.

Let us know what you think. Thanks!

Best,
